    {
      "id": "PopularPost364787",
      "post_content": "I find this card to be criminally underrated right now. While it has no use in any other format, in limited it becomes a winner. With the lack of straight up removal in Theros, +2/+2 is a pretty big buff. After that, giving a repeatable \"can't block\" ability to the creature as well is better, meaning your big creature gets to swing in for with little to no hassle or you force them to block with their important creature. This basically won me the launch day tournament!.... except I didn't cause I failed to choose the right creatures with the ability.",
      "posted_by": "Bazzoka",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost364787\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">I find this card to be criminally underrated right now. While it has no use in any other format, in limited it becomes a winner. With the lack of straight up removal in Theros, +2/+2 is a pretty big buff. After that, giving a repeatable \"can't block\" ability to the creature as well is better, meaning your big creature gets to swing in for with little to no hassle or you force them to block with their important creature. This basically won me the launch day tournament!.... except I didn't cause I failed to choose the right creatures with the ability.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '364787'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy13605\">Bazzoka</span>\r\n                                (2/21/2014 1:43:51 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSm